------------------------------------------------

DATABASE DESIGN

Use PocketBase collections.

Required entities:

restaurants

tables

reservations

customers

Tables must include positional coordinates so they can be rendered inside the visual restaurant floor plan.

------------------------------------------------

FLOOR PLAN SYSTEM

The system must include an interactive restaurant floor plan showing tables.

Tables should have:

table number

capacity

position (x,y)

shape

area

Status colors:

green = available

yellow = reserved

red = occupied

The floor plan should allow:

visual rendering

reservation assignment

table selection

optional drag-and-drop positioning

------------------------------------------------

TABLE ASSIGNMENT LOGIC

When a reservation is created the system should suggest the best table based on:

number of guests

table capacity

table availability

minimal unused capacity

